{"about_the_game":"In Spookville: Cabin Escape, players step into the shoes of a courageous protagonist determined to save their parents from the clutches of a malevolent force. The tranquil setting of a cozy cabin nestled deep within the dark woods becomes a nightmarish battleground as a wicked scarecrow emerges as the primary antagonist.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792360/extras/werewolf_optimized.gif?t=1720445362\" /><br><br>Armed with cunning intellect and an arsenal of cleverly concealed tools, players must navigate through a series of spine-tingling puzzles, uncover hidden secrets, and face hair-raising challenges. Use your anthropomorphic Teddy Bear to your advantage with the ability to give commands such as &quot;Stay&quot;, and &quot;Follow Me!&quot;.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792360/extras/teddy_cropped_optimized.gif?t=1720445362\" /><br><br>Will you have what it takes to outsmart the scarecrow and rescue your parents from an unimaginable fate? Gather resources and build structures during the day to protect your cabin from attacks at night. Find the hidden lair of the evil scarecrow and save your parents from an unfathomable demise.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792360/extras/mountain.gif?t=1720445362\" /><br><br>Get ready to embark on an unforgettable journey filled with fear, suspense, and ultimately, triumph.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792360/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1720445362","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792360/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1720445362","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2792360/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1720445362","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steams